# AI Technical Portfolio

This repository contains sample work demonstrating technical knowledge across multiple domains relevant to AI training and model evaluation projects.

The goal of this portfolio is to provide examples of structured reasoning, technical documentation, and domain-specific analysis used in AI training workflows.

## Domains Covered

### Game Development (Godot Engine)
Example scripts demonstrating gameplay programming, player movement systems, and basic AI behaviors using GDScript.

### Geospatial Analysis (QGIS)
Examples of spatial data workflows including map visualization, coordinate systems, and geographic data interpretation.

### Legal Research and Reasoning
Examples of legal analysis, structured argument evaluation, and case reasoning methods.

### Technical Analysis
Examples of analytical approaches used for evaluating data, systems, and technical outputs.

